Legoshi.

00:20:25.015 --> 00:20:26.058
Legoshi.

00:20:26.934 --> 00:20:28.769
Aoba, sedang apa kau di sini?

00:20:30.813 --> 00:20:32.314
Aku kabur dari sana.

00:20:33.315 --> 00:20:37.236
Aku tak bisa makan jari orang tua itu.

00:20:39.822 --> 00:20:44.744
Saat aku memikirkan
teman herbivoraku seperti Sanu dan Rouis,

00:20:45.327 --> 00:20:47.997
itu membuatku sangat mual.

00:20:49.832 --> 00:20:51.417
<i>Aoba...</i>

00:20:52.418 --> 00:20:53.836
<i>Bahkan di saat seperti ini,</i>

00:20:53.919 --> 00:20:58.758
<i>paruh karnivoramu tampak</i>
<i>sangat tajam dan indah.</i>

00:21:05.181 --> 00:21:08.726
Maaf soal tadi.

00:21:08.809 --> 00:21:09.769
Ayo kembali...

00:21:13.272 --> 00:21:14.982
Legoshi, apa kau menangis...

00:21:15.858 --> 00:21:17.777
Aku tak punya saputangan.

00:21:17.860 --> 00:21:18.778
Kau tak apa-apa?

00:21:19.695 --> 00:21:21.155
<i>Aku mau berdiri sendiri.</i>

00:21:21.906 --> 00:21:25.451
<i>Dengan kakiku yang bercakar di dunia ini.</i>

00:21:26.076 --> 00:21:27.703
<i>Aku dan Aoba hanya ingin</i>

00:21:28.621 --> 00:21:31.999
